1. ID
2. Summary/Title
3. Description
4. Steps to reproduce
5. Expected result
6. Actual result
7. Severity
8. Priority
9. Label
10.Workaround
11.Comments
12.Attachments


In addition to the standart bug report fields, depending on bug tracking system we can add

13. Author ( of bug)
14. Assigned to ( developer, who work with this part of product)
15. Status ( Show current stage of working withe the bug ( New, assigned, re-open, verified etc.)
16. Creation date ( date of creating bug report)
17. Environment